            <lg xml:id="TK268">
<l>taṉṉuyir tāṉaṟap peṟṟāṉai yēṉaiya</l>
<l>maṉṉuyi rellān toḻum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All other creatures will worship him who has attained the control of his own soul.</l>
